cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI

This paper proposes a new method for combining ensembles of base classifiers using a special neural network. The paper focuses on improving the efficiency of classification, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves image classification, which falls under the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the proposed method involves adaptive and efficient fusion, which could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
